rows.label: qev093102_MSG0010
rows.name: Slowpoke. What took you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0020
rows.name: As much as I'd like to launch straight in,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0025
rows.name:
it's hard to get amped about a battle
with no stakes, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0030
rows.name: Right! Let's do this:[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0040
rows.name:
If you can win this match, you get to ask
one favor of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0050
rows.name:
It's only fair, since I picked this fight.
Call it a bonus.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0060
rows.name: Well? Got something in mind?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_JNK0070
rows.name: Demand

rows.label: qev093102_SEL0080
rows.name: Say that you want the Ares.

rows.label: qev093102_JNK0090
rows.name: Request

rows.label: qev093102_SEL0100
rows.name: Ask to take the Ares for a spin.

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0110
rows.name: Whoa whoa, hold the phone now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0120
rows.name:
You're really telling me to hand over Ares?
Like ripping a babe from its mother's arms?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0130
rows.name: Just to be clear...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0140
rows.name:
You won't be able to pilot him
without your real body, you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0150
rows.name: You SURE you still want this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0160
rows.name:
Damn... You're a real character. Might even give
Princess a good run for her money, you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0170
rows.name: But...I like it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0180
rows.name:
You're hyping this up so much now,
it's hard not to get fired up about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0190
rows.name:
Though, if you really wanna take Ares from me,
you better believe I'll make you sweat blood for it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093102_MSG0200
rows.name: I want you to give me...all you've got.[ST:wait ]
